ame=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up || [[1926 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1926]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Ren\u00e9 Lacoste]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Elizabeth Ryan]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean Borotra]] || 4\u20136, 5\u20137 ||<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up || [[1927 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1927]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Ren\u00e9 Lacoste]] || {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Eileen Bennett]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Henri Cochet]] || 2\u20136, 6\u20130, 3\u20136 ||\n|}\n\n==Grand Slam singles tournament timeline==\n{{performance key|short=yes|active=no}}\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#efefef\"\n! Tournament !! 1909 !! 1910 !! 1911 !! 1912 \u2013 1914!! 1915 !! 1916 \u2013 1918 !! 1919 !! 1920 !! 1921 !! 1922 !! 1923 !! 1924 !! 1925 !! 1926 !! 1927 !! 1928 !! Career SR\n|-\n| style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[Australian Open (tennis)|Australian Championships]]\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" | NH\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | '''0 / 0'''\n|-\n| style=\"background:#EFEFEF;\" | [[French Open (tennis)|French Championships]]<sup>*</sup>\n| align=\"center\" |R\n| align=\"center\" |R\n| align=\"center\" |R\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |NH\n| align=\"center\" |NH\n| align=\"center\" |NH\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |NH\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"center\" |A\n| align=\"