 F. Johnson|Wallace Johnson]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Edna Wildey]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Herbert Morris Tilden]] || 6\u20134, 6\u20134 ||<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner || [[1915 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1915]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|USA}} [[Harry Johnson (tennis)|Harry Johnson]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Molla Mallory|Molla Bjurstedt]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Irving Wright]] || 6\u20130, 6\u20131 ||<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner || [[1918 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1918]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|USA}} [[Irving Wright]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Molla Mallory|Molla Bjurstedt]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Fred Alexander]] || 6\u20132, 6\u20133 ||<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner || [[1920 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1920]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|USA}} [[Wallace F. Johnson|Wallace Johnson]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Molla Mallory|Molla Bjurstedt Mallory]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Craig Biddle]] || 6\u20134, 6\u20133 ||<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up || [[1926 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1926]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Ren\u00e9 Lacoste]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Elizabeth Ryan]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Jean Borotra]] || 4\u20136, 5\u20137 ||<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-style=\"background:#ccf;\"\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up || [[1927 U.S. National Championships (tennis)|1927]] || [[US Open (tennis)|U.S. National Championships]] || Grass ||  {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Ren\u00e9 Lacoste]] || {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Eileen Bennett]]<br>{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Henri Cochet]] || 2\u20136, 6\u20130, 3\u20136 ||\n|}\n\n==Grand Slam