]'''\n|-\n| align=left bgcolor=#efefef|[[Australian Open]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1958 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|1R]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1960 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|1R]]\n| bgcolor=yellow|[[1961 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|SF]]\n| bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1962 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|QF]]\n| bgcolor=yellow|[[1963 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|SF]]\n| bgcolor=thistle|[[1964 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|F]]\n| bgcolor=thistle|[[1965 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|F]]\n| bgcolor=yellow|[[1966 Australian Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|SF]]\n| A\n| A\n| bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1969 Australian Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|QF]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1971 Australian Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|3R]]\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| bgcolor=#efefef| 0 / 10\n|-\n| align=left bgcolor=#efefef|[[French Open]]\n| A\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1960 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1961 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|3R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1962 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|4R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1963 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1964 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|4R]]\n| bgcolor=lime|[[1965 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|'''W''']]\n| bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1966 French Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|QF]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1968 French Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1969 French Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|QF]]\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n|  colspan=2|A\n| A\n| bgcolor=#efefef| 1 / 9\n|-\n| align=left bgcolor=#efefef|[[The Championships, Wimbledon|Wimbledon]]\n| A\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1960 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|1R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1961 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1962 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|3R]]\n| bgcolor=thistle|[[1963 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|F]]\n| bgcolor=thistle|[[1964 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|F]]\n| bgcolor=thistle|[[1965 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|F]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1966 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1968 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|4R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1969 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|4R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1970 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|1R]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1971 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|4R]]\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n|  colspan=2|A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1978 Wimbledon Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|1R]]\n| bgcolor=#efefef| 0 / 12\n|-\n| align=left bgcolor=#efefef|[[US Open (tennis)|US Open]]\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1962 U.S. National Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=thistle|[[1964 U.S. National Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|F]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1965 U.S. National Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| bgcolor=lime|[[1966 U.S. National Championships  \u2013 Men's Singles|'''W''']]\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1968 US Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1969 US Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|QF]]\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1970 US Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|3R]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=ffebcd|[[1972 US Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|QF]]\n| A\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee|[[1975 US Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|1R]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=afeeee colspan=2|[[1977 US Open  \u2013 Men's Singles|2R]]\n| A\n| bgcolor=#efefef| 1 / 10\n|- style=\"font-weight:bold; background:#efefef;\"\n| style=text-align:left|Strike Rate\n| 0 / 1\n| 0 / 0\n| 0 / 3\n| 0 / 3\n| 0 / 4\n| 0 / 3\n| 0 / 4\n| 1 / 4\n| 1 / 4\n| 0 / 0\n| 0 / 3\n| 0 / 4\n| 0 / 2\n| 0 / 2\n| 0 / 1\n| 0 / 0\n| 0 / 0\n| 0 / 1\n| 0 / 0\n|  colspan=2|0 / 1\n| 0 / 1\n| {{nowrap|2 / 41}}\n|}\nNote: The Australian Open was held twice in 1977, in January and December.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{ATP}}\n* {{ITF}}\n* {{Davis Cup player}}\n* {{Tennis Hall of Fame}}\n* {{Tennis Australia}}\n\n{{navboxes|title=Fred Stolle in the [[Grand Slam (tennis)|Grand Slam Tournaments]]\n| list1 = \n{{French Open men's singles champions}}\n{{US Open men's singles champions}}\n{{Australian Championships men's doubles champions}}\n{{French Open men's doubles champions}}\n{{Wimbledon men's doubles champions}}\n{{U.S. National Championships Men's doubles champions}}\n{{Australian Championships mixed doubles champions}}\n{{Wimbledon mixed doubles champions}}\n{{U.S. National Championships mixed doubles champions}}\n{{US Open men's doubles champions}}\n{{Australian Open mixed doubles champions}}\n}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Stolle, Fred}}\n[[Category:Australian Championships (tennis) champions]]\n[[Category:Australian male tennis players]]\n[[Category:Australian Open (tennis) champions]]\n[[Category:French Championships (tennis) champions]]\n[[Category:French Open champions]]\n[[Category:People from the North Shore, Sydney]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Sydney]]\n[[Category:Tennis people from New South Wales]]\n[[Category:Australian tennis commentators]]\n[[Category:Officers of the Order of Australia]]\n[[Category:Recipients of the Australian Sports Medal]]\n[[Category:International Tennis Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:Sport Australia Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:United States National champions (tennis)]]\n[[Category:US Open (tennis) champions]]\n[[Category:Wimbledon champions]]\n[[Category:Wimbledon champions (pre-Open Era)]]\n[[Category:1938 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Grand Slam (tennis) champions in men's singles]]\n[[Category:Grand Slam (tennis) champions in mixed doubles]]\n[[Category:Grand Slam (tennis) champions in men's doubles]]\n[[Category:Professional tennis players before the Open Era]]\n[[Category:Australian people of German descent]]\n", "name_user": "Wolbo", "label": "safe", "